ated businesses during  we also repaid approximately  million of debt and significantly strengthened our balance sheet form  venator materials corporations registration statement on form  is available on venators website at wwwvenatorcorpcom and the secs website at wwwsecgov the completion of the spinoff is subject to the satisfaction or waiver of a number of conditions including the registration statement on form  for venator materials corporations common stock being declared effective by the sec and certain other conditions described in the information statement included in the form  to request a copy of the venator logo email karenfenwickhuntsmancom conference call information we will hold a conference call to discuss this announcement on tuesday january   at  am et callin numbers for the conference callus participants    international participants    passcode    in order to facilitate the registration process you may use the following link to preregister for the conference call callers who preregister will be given a unique pin to gain immediate access to the call and bypass the live operator you may preregister at any time including up to and after the call start time to preregister please go to httpswwwtheconferencingservicecompreregkeyprocesskeypfwprkne webcast information the conference call will be available via webcast and can be accessed from the companys website at irhuntsmancom replay information the conference call will be available for replay beginning january   and ending january   callin numbers for the replayus participants    international participants    replay code  about huntsmanhuntsman corporation is a publicly traded global manufacturer and marketer of differentiated chemicals with  revenues of more than  billion our chemical products number in the thousands and are sold worldwide to manufacturers serving a broad and diverse range of consumer and industrial end markets we operate more than  manufacturing and rd facilities in approximately  c