man to spin off pigments business wednesday november   more items for coatings technology  more huntsman corporation an americanbased global chemical manufacturer with more than  billion in revenue last year is looking to move ahead with a plan to spin off its pigments  additives business into its own company with a focus on titanium dioxide the woodlands txbased manufacturer which produces products including polyurethanes and epoxies filed an initial form  registration statement with the us securities and exchange commission oct  it said when announcing its third quarter financial results form  also known as the general form for registration of securities is used to register securities for trading on us exchanges and is used by analysts and private investors when making investment decisions huntsman huntsman corporation has announced it has filed the necessary paperwork to continue with plans to spin off its pigments  additives division a new publicly traded company “this filing represents an important step in the progression towards a separation” president and ceo peter r huntsman said in a statement “subject to market conditions we plan to separate in the first half of ” the subsidiary temporarily named huntsman spin corporation also includes its textile effects business profitable segment the plan to spin off rather than sell the business was announced in july after the pigments and additives business became profitable again following a period of poor performance when business was down huntsman attempted to distance itself from the titanium dioxide tio business according to the houston chronicle and even began eliminate about  jobs in  primarily at most of them at three tio manufacturing plants in germany and finland however once business improved the company determined it would be better served to spin off the unit and sell shares instead of selling it outright huntsman’s form  included a business overview market information company strengths and strategy certain named executive management and historical carveout financial statements based on the filing the pigments spinoff company will be based in stocktonontees uk chemical industry information provider icis reported the new entity will reportedly operate  facilities with  employees catering to approximately  customers in more than  countries focus on tio the spinoff business will focus primarily on tio production with an anticipated production capacity of  tonnes a year it said by benjahbmm  public domain via wikimedia commons the spinoff business will focus primarily on tio production with a production capacity expected to place it as one of three largest titanium dioxide producers in the world according to icis this will position the spinoff as one of three largest producers in the world contributing  percent of global capacity although the company said it saw seasonally lower volumes for additives products in the third quarter it reported an increase in end use demand for its titanium dioxide products  “tio prices are improving and with additional increases expected in the future the timing of our spinoff should be well positioned” huntsman said in addition to tio the spinoff is also slated to produce color pigments functional additives timbertreatment products and watertreatment chemicals the spinoffs pigments and additives segment will reportedly operate  plants in  countries with a total capacity of  million tonnes per year this includes plans for  colorpigment manufacturing and processing plants which will make ironoxide and other pigments additionally it will have a functional additives facility in europe this area includes barium and zincbased inorganic chemicals used to make colors brighter coatings shine and protect against fading icis explained executive structure according to the filing simon turner who is now division president of huntsmans pigment business will take on the role of ceo kurt ogden vice president of investor relations will become chief financial officer the chief operating officer will be rohit aggarwal he is currently the division president of huntsmans textileeffects business additional information regarding capitalization additional pro forma information and other matters will be provided in subsequent amendments to the form  the company said a final company name is expected to be announced in the first quarter of  tweet     tagged categories additives business matters business operations coatings raw materials manufacturers huntsman pigments raw materials titanium dioxide join the conversation sign in to our community to add your comments advertisements     kta analyzes coating failures   • field diagnosis • lab diagnosis • determination of cause • recommendations wwwktacom        speedhide® proev zero interior paint   for a dependable vocfree interior paint professionals who are both performanceconscious and costconscious rely on ppg paints™ speedhide proev zero       trusted performance with proven results   pratt  lambert’s finest accolade® premium paint  primer applies flawlessly with superb hide and longlasting durability for great results every time       vitreflon – the hallmark of colour stable protective coatings   vitreflon two pack fluoropolymer coatings display unsurpassed colour and gloss retention making vitreflon the coating of choice for high value infrastructure and architecture contact us today to find out how vitreflon can outperform on your next project vitreflon distributorships available       helping you put your products to the test   outdoor accelerated weathering laboratory testing services accelerated weathering instruments wwwatlasmtscomatlasinfoametekcom         technology publishing co  reedsdale street suite  pittsburgh pa  tel   bullet fax    bullet  email webmasterdurabilityanddesigncom the technology publishing network about dd  contact us  advertise  news  blogs  resources  buying guides  classifieds subscribe  privacy policy  terms  conditions  site map  search  